4. **`git-workflow.js`** (7.9KB)
   - Git operations automation
   - Creates git hooks and workflows
   - Prepares commit and push operations
   - Generates git workflow reports

5. **`execute-automation.js`** (1.2KB)
   - Simple execution wrapper
